Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.71,1:09:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,心空了  没有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.34,1:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.49,1:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.92,1:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.35,1:10:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在上面干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.67,1:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛  快下来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.01,1:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爬到上面去干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.84,1:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  迟到了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.22,1:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.83,1:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.50,1:10:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,霍尔克先生走了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.53,1:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,去新西兰教画画了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.24,1:11:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来了一个新的代课老师
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.78,1:11:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他跟霍尔克先生不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.22,1:11:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  要迟到了  快点
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.91,1:13:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看  那是棵树吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.02,1:13:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还是披着斗篷的人
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.99,1:13:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.65,1:13:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还是天空忘了关水龙头
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.58,1:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,世界由你自己创造
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.32,1:13:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一切尽在你眼中
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.87,1:13:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以解放思想
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.89,1:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,舒展心灵翅膀
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.80,1:13:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让色彩飞翔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.82,1:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  来吧  编织新的梦想
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.87,1:14:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.82,1:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,幻想
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.63,1:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,多美好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.61,1:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快去努力吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.49,1:14:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来
